title: Jane Fonda's New Workout
brief_description: Jane Fonda’s chart topping fitness tape finally makes it to Australia. Includes a 35 minute beginners class with 12 minutes of aerobics and a 55 minute advanced class with 16 minutes of aerobics. Voted most popular “How to” video for 1986 in the USA. Rated: G
